{"tid":324155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★IT出頭天！調查指香港家長希望子女長大後做IT !","createTime":"2017-07-16T08:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T04:20:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef181692810ae873b919f1792beaadd13b5a2477","tid":324155,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"有機構進行的家長及幼童對未來職場調查顯示，逾3成受訪兒童希望長大後當明星及創業，近4成兒童希望長大後能賺多些錢。<br />\n<br />\n調查以問卷形式，訪問了423名育有4至8歲小孩的家長及其子女，近四成兒童表示希望長大後能賺多些錢，所以選擇從事明星，電腦或科技業及紀律部隊等行業。另外，近3成受訪父母對子女將來的工作沒有要求，願意讓子女自行選擇。<br />\n<br />\n負責調查的香港家庭教育學院總監余榮輝認為，小孩子的想法是較天真和天馬行空，建議家長毋須太早否定他們的想法，反而可以先了解他們選擇該職業的原因，幫助孩子發掘才能。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，不少兒童選擇理想職業時，都以錢作為衡量因素，他建議家長應從他們就讀幼稚園開始，教導子女認識和管理金錢，並可以讓他們參加職業體驗，令他們認識上班的概念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/161410_c26a1b5e576162e10f43ce78e972b098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F161410_c26a1b5e576162e10f43ce78e972b098.jpg&h=c4fa8734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1342431-20170716.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1342431-20170716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aXcLiUvFnzfo6nRO7BKCjuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=a6dc76f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1342431-20170716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=43cbf8be\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1342431-20170716.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6f7033498c1d6f30bccf749057caa80a975bff2e","tid":324155,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/161614_b74499360b583e780d31e5ef28a42da4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F161614_